              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "Futuristic Auditorium & Training Hub",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "For Canadian University Dubai, a new auditorium and innovation hub was designed to serve as both the university’s formal ceremonial hall and a training ground for the next generation of marketers and brand builders. With a capacity of 200–300, the space embodies a futuristic, VIP atmosphere aligned with the university’s innovative spirit.",
              "spans": []
            }
